    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Poles, masts, or structures mounted with one or more electric lamps of high wattage. Generally permanently fixed for use in stadiums, light towers also exist as mobile units used in the construction industry.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
